"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-paris-2024-which-events-are-there-still-tickets-for-at-the-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  With the Paris 2024 Olympics just over a week away fans are still, incredibly, able to get their hands on hundreds of tickets.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some are for the biggest events while others are for lesser supported sports.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here atCity A.M.we have broken where the value is, and where can you get bang for your buck in comparison to the size and status of the various events at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the showpiece event of any Olympic Games, where the fastest men in the world compete for glory.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The iconic Stade de France will host this year's final with tickets for the evening session on Sunday 4 August ranging from \\u00a3245 in Category C to \\u00a3820 at Category A.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's astonishing there are tickets still available.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if you want to be in with a shot of seeing a Team GB gold intrack and field, try catching Keely Hodgkinson in the 800m final on 5 August.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets range from \\u00a3163 in Category D to \\u00a3830 in Category First.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Football may not have come home but, incredibly, you can watch the Euro 2024 champions open their quest for gold at the home of PSG - the Parc des Princes - for just \\u00a342.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure they are taking on Uzbekistan, but the beautiful game in the City of Light for slightly more than an away day ticket in the Premier League is not to be sniffed at.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.7140190704194758, \"rank\": 0.3651001095112195, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}, {\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.0303799108340026e-11, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other venues across France include Lyon, Bordeaux, Marseille and Nice with Category A tickets still available for the final in Paris - though Kylian Mbappe will not be there.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999883179954, \"rank\": 1.0954496704217314e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 0.9951141025976737, \"rank\": 0.0049098866029943285, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"score\": 0.9999996547840652, \"rank\": 3.4521600583252796e-07, \"text\": \"Bordeaux\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9998325364750519, \"rank\": 0.00016749157352507137, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OGC_Nice\", \"score\": 0.999724038975797, \"rank\": 0.0002760371997484905, \"text\": \"Nice\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OGC_Nice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OGC_Nice\"}, {\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0236788837754477e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P